        <footnote id="F1">On February 23, 2016, the Reporting Person was granted 1,630 (target) performance-based restricted stock units (&quot;PBRSUs&quot;) pursuant to the Issuer's 2014 Long-Term Incentive Plan. The PBRSUs were subject to both performance-based and time-based vesting conditions. On December 30, 2018, the Issuer announced the issuance of a $4.75 special dividend payable on January 25, 2019 to all shareholders of record on January 10, 2019 (the &quot;Special Dividend&quot;). On January 9, 2019, the target amount of the PBRSUs was automatically adjusted to reflect the Special Dividend. On January 23, 2019, the performance condition for this award was certified at 115.38% of the target award, vesting the performance condition of the PBRSUs and converting the award into a restricted stock unit for the number of shares indicated. The restricted stock unit will vest 100% on the third anniversary of the original PBRSU grant date.</footnote>
